strings: <voice_0x01000BAF><se_low>January: I hear! We haven't done anything wrong!
<voice_0x01000BB0><se_high>Accuracy: There are a lot of people here! we will tell you! Discover healing here!
<voice_0x01000BB1><se_high>Accuracy: By what right have you locked us here?
<voice_0x01000BB2><se_def>awesome!: ... Monks are very patient. if I am innocent, which hurts my husband
<voice_0x01000BB3><se_def>awesome!: Otherwise, I don't know. You can't fool me so don't even try.
<voice_0x01000BB4><se_def>awesome!: who is this person
<voice_0x01000BB5><se_def>*: please call me captain
<voice_0x01000BB6><se_def>awesome!: Within!
<voice_0x01000BB7><se_def>awesome!: I have a question but one thing before...
<voice_0x01000BB8><se_def>awesome!: In one of the monasteries we meet with a bandit. they want to kill her.
<voice_0x01000BB9><se_def>awesome!: Among my people, 6 people were injured.
<voice_0x01000BBA>awesome!: .........
<voice_0x01000BBB><se_def>awesome!: Okay, moving on to the next question...
<voice_0x01000BBC><se_def>awesome!: Outsiders suffered from lack of water in the garden and outsiders could not enter the temple.
<voice_0x01000BBD><se_def>awesome!: Unless, of course, the internet helps...
<voice_0x01000BBE><se_def>awesome!: Do you believe so or not? While searching your domain we found this ring.
<voice_0x01000BBF><se_def>awesome!: Angel Knights! tell me where your ring is I'm with you
<voice_0x01000BC0><se_def>China: Yes, here we go! Thank you very much Dev!
<voice_0x01000BC1><se_def>awesome!: ... that too! one
<voice_0x01000BC2><se_def>China: I was mugged at the bar. They seem to understand that crime is valuable.
<voice_0x01000BC3><se_low>January: He caught one! some fibre!
<voice_0x01000BC4><se_high>Accuracy: There are no more rings! we called!
<voice_0x01000BC5><se_high>Accuracy: I wish I had known better not to take in a fool like you!
<voice_0x01000BC6><se_def>China: I don't have anything more to say now. you will find me in my room
<voice_0x01000BC7><se_def>awesome!: How often will our work be incomplete!
<voice_0x01000BC8><se_def>awesome!: he was! I'll explain it later. Firstly.
<voice_0x01000BC9><se_def>awesome!: ... You're wasting your time. Don't test my patience! I'd like to hear your opinion!
<voice_0x01000BCA><se_def>awesome!: It depends on what you do with Pisces!
<voice_0x01000BCB><se_low>January: We have nothing to admit!
<voice_0x01000BCC><se_def>awesome!: also
<voice_0x01000BCD><se_def>*: You've discovered a strange creature hidden behind the monastery!
<voice_0x01000BCE><se_def>awesome!: what is that? What a beast!
<voice_0x01000BCF><se_low>King of tricks: I mean that seriously! what are you doing now !
<voice_0x01000BD0><se_low>King of tricks: Hello <Cap><hero> Jessica, oh my! what are you doing here
<voice_0x01000BD1><se_low>King of tricks: It's been a while and I'm a little worried. Therefore, I decided to visit you ...
<voice_0x01000BD2><se_def>awesome!: ...so these monsters are your friends! Only intelligent people!
<voice_0x01000BD3><se_low>King of tricks: You are in trouble. Leave her behind. The arrogant starlet! Get out <hero>!
<voice_0x01000BD4><se_def>awesome!: You're dating the devil in secret. Father Francis may have had an affair. But you didn't lie to me!
<voice_0x01000BD5><se_def>awesome!: The devil told you to steal the ring and get into the temple? cursed heretic!
<voice_0x01000BD6><se_def>awesome!: You think you can shock the whole world by killing the abbot? Find out what you believe! I think it puts you in more control and gives you control.
<voice_0x01000BD7><se_def>awesome!: Face monsters in the dungeons!
<voice_0x01000BD8><se_def>awesome!: I'll torture him enough tomorrow. Then you will know the seriousness of sin.
<voice_0x01000BD9><se_def>awesome!: ... Sweet dreams before dawn!
